captions.text:
So, let's play a game that I really like:
"Questions Only."

Everybody will play "Questions Only",
stand up please.
Anderson and Rafinha will begin.

It will be a little contest: Anderson and Tas
versus Rafinha and Elidio.
They can only talk by asking questions.

If someone takes too long to ask a question,
or doesn't ask a question...
Hadouken!

If someone takes too long to ask a question,
or doesn't ask a question...

We'll ring the bell, and
another player will step up.

To do that, I need
another place. Anything.
Circus.
Gay sauna. He's here.
Give it up for the Gay Sauna Man!

I thought he wouldn't get here
after Madonna's concert.
Circus.
Traffic...
It's "Questions Only", you're in traffic. Go.
Got some small change, sir?
Why would you want some small change?
Don't you wanna help me?
You're needing help now?
How much?

Didn't you see what's
in front of you?
Buyin' anything, chief?
Are you talking to me?
Want some bubble gum?
Didn't you see my car?
Didn't you see his car, man?
Go, Felipe Massa!
"Go, Felipe Massa."
Come back, Rafinha!
He's back!

Too bad he's back
with his pants down.
Traffic,"Questions Only", go.

Hey buddy, what's the deal
with this horning?

Couldn't you move
to the other lane?
Can't you see it's all jammed?

Why don't you take
the freeway?

Can't you see we're in
the other side of the city?
Would you know the way to the freeway?

IMPROVÁVEL
Probably a good show.
